nl.inl.blacklab.perdocument

Class DocProperty

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.inl.blacklab.perdocument.DocProperty
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DocPropertyComplexFieldLength, DocPropertyDecade, DocPropertyMultiple, DocPropertyNumberOfHits, DocPropertyStoredField

    public abstract class DocProperty
extends Object
    Abstract base class for criteria on which to group DocResult objects. Subclasses implement specific grouping criteria (number of hits, the value of a stored field in the Lucene document, ...)
